Do you hear me?
Go to your side, now!

00:21:48.910 --> 00:21:52.345 position:10% line:83% align:start
All right. I've understood.
I'm sorry.

00:21:52.379 --> 00:21:54.715 position:10% line:89% align:start
That player was Makoto Soda.

